  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Economic Report 2023 Q3\nStar Atlas published their latest economic report.\nStar Atlas Recap September 29th 2023\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recap of the latest in Star Atlas.\nStar Atlas Economy – R4 Supply and Demand (Aephia DataRunners)\nUndisputed Noobs posted a video looking at the R4 supply and demand.\nMost people playing Star Atlas are missing this MASSIVE advantage / Weekly Recap\nUndisputed Noobs posted a video recap of the latest in Star Atlas.\nMetaverse Nomads #114 Star Atlas w/ Chypto\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video replay of their Star Atlas livestream.\nStar Atlas Ships – Introducing the Fimbul ECOS Unibomba\nStar Atlas posted a video of the Fimbul ECOS Unibomba.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #99\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nThe latest Star Atlas news and drops!!\nAtlas Theory posted a video about the latest Star Atlas news.\nStar Atlas Chatter #15 – Chypto’s ALPHA & Game IDs?\nRahMega posted a video with news of Star Atlas.\n#12 | BACK… To Escape Velocity | Star Atlas\nPathfinder posted a video about his experiences in Star Atlas SAGE Labs.\nStar Atlas Opens Doors to Free Development for Solana Builders and Creators in SAGE Labs and Beyond\nStar Atlas published an article about open-platforming its developer tools.\nThe Atlas Brew #82\nStar Atlas TV posted a video replay of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas Brew #82: SAGE Labs w/ Economics Team\nTLDR 3.0 posted a recap of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas Sage Labs Week 2 And SDU’s\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about his experiences in SAGE Labs.\nStar Atlas: Let’s Go Shopping!\nOCG Thor posted a video about a Star Atlas tool he is building.",
